# Habit Tracker API

A FastAPI-based habit tracking backend with authentication, authorization, 
daily habit completion, and progress tracking.

## Features
- JWT Authentication
- User-specific habit management
- Daily habit completion
- Todayâ€™s habit status API

## Tech Stack
- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy
- PostgreSQL
- Alembic
- JWT Auth

## Run locally
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
